ZH: 我喜欢在花园里种植百合。
EN: I like planting lilies in the garden.

ZH: 这束花里有红玫瑰和白百合。
EN: This bouquet includes red roses and white lilies.

ZH: 那片草地上开满了野百合。
EN: The field is full of wild lilies.

ZH: 我们家的花园里有一丛丛粉色的百合。
EN: In our garden, there are clusters of pink lilies.

ZH: 今年的百合开得格外美丽。
EN: The lilies this year bloomed particularly beautifully.

ZH: 她最喜欢的花是百合。
EN: Her favorite flower is the lily.

ZH: 孩子们在田野里捡到了一束野百合。
EN: The children picked a bunch of wild lilies in the field.

ZH: 春天到了，百合开始盛开。
EN: Spring has arrived and the lilies are in full bloom.

ZH: 每年清明节，人们都会到野外采集野百合。
EN: Every year during Qingming Festival, people go to the fields to collect wild lilies.

ZH: 百合花有一种淡淡的清香。
EN: The lily flower has a faint fragrance.

ZH: 你知道吗？百合象征着纯洁和高贵。
EN: Do you know? The lily symbolizes purity and nobility.

ZH: 百合花语是“纯真美好”。
EN: The language of lilies is "pure and beautiful".

ZH: 她的婚礼上用了很多百合作为装饰。
EN: Many lilies were used as decorations at her wedding.

ZH: 百合花的颜色种类丰富，有白色、粉色、黄色等。
EN: Lilies come in a variety of colors, including white, pink, and yellow.

ZH: 百合花是很多人最喜欢的花之一。
EN: Lilies are a favorite flower for many people.

ZH: 这个公园里有很多不同种类的百合花。
EN: There are many different types of lilies in this park.

ZH: 她在花瓶里插上了一枝鲜艳的百合。
EN: She placed a bright lily in a vase.

ZH: 这家餐厅的装饰上挂满了百合花。
EN: The decorations in this restaurant are filled with lilies.

ZH: 昨晚我做了一个美丽的百合花盘。
EN: Last night I made a beautiful lily arrangement.

ZH: 他送给她一束粉色的百合花来表示感谢。
EN: He gave her a bouquet of pink lilies as a token of gratitude.
